snippet.title: Toys Gets Stuck On Mom's Face | Diana and Roma
snippet.description:
Toys get stuck on mom's face all the time and it's up to  Diana Roma and Oliver to learn how to clean them up.
With a little bit of help from mom, they'll be able to keep their home clean and tidy. 
By following the tips in this video, children will learn the importance of cleaning up their toys and avoid getting into trouble with mom.
